# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:2
translate chinese u20f_7d92946f:

    # "For now, I should go see Mari."
    "现在，我该去看看玛丽了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:5
translate chinese u20f_2bb3b023:

    # "I drive to Mari's house and knock on her door."
    "我开车来到玛丽家，敲了敲门。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:6
translate chinese u20f_0b175aad:

    # "Her dogs start barking at the door and I hear footsteps approaching."
    "她的狗开始在门边狂吠，我听到脚步声走近。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:7
translate chinese u20f_be91a4c9:

    # fr "Who is it?"
    fr "是谁？"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:8
translate chinese u20f_1063bb8b:

    # pc "It's me! [pcname]."
    pc "是我！[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:12
translate chinese u20f_a9b3d399:

    # fr "Oh my God, [pcname]!"
    fr "天哪，[pcname]！"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:13
translate chinese u20f_ea03fec2:

    # "She opens the door and stares at me for a moment, shocked."
    "她打开门，震惊地盯着我看了片刻。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:14
translate chinese u20f_40412d0f:

    # "I can see her eyes welling up with tears."
    "我看到她的眼睛里涌出了泪水。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:15
translate chinese u20f_23647146:

    # fr "I thought..."
    fr "我还以为……"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:18
translate chinese u20f_540e25ed:

    # "She rushes into my arms and hugs me tightly."
    "她扑进我怀里，紧紧地抱住了我。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:19
translate chinese u20f_140e4956:

    # "I hug her back, feeling her warmth and the softness of her body."
    "我也回抱了她，感受着她的体温和身体的柔软。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:20
translate chinese u20f_dddaeb84:

    # pc "I missed you, Mari. I'm sorry I was gone for so long."
    pc "我想你了，玛丽。对不起，我离开这么久。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:23
translate chinese u20f_b77230d2:

    # fr "I was so worried about you. I thought that machine killed you."
    fr "我一直很担心你。我还以为那台机器把你害死了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:24
translate chinese u20f_40e4fe9b:

    # pc "I fought so hard to get back."
    pc "我拼尽全力才回来。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:25
translate chinese u20f_356f7f42:

    # pc "I'll tell you everything tomorrow, I promise."
    pc "明天我全都告诉你，我保证。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:28
translate chinese u20f_e5e85df6:

    # fr "I'm just glad you're back."
    fr "我只是很高兴你回来了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:29
translate chinese u20f_1f943087:

    # fr "Wow, your hair grew a lot."
    fr "哇，你的头发长长了好多。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:30
translate chinese u20f_c49af8d0:

    # fr "It makes you look all rugged."
    fr "这让你看起来特别有男子气概。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:33
translate chinese u20f_7d64063d:

    # "She kisses me softly, her lips warm and inviting."
    "她轻轻吻了我一下，她的双唇温暖而诱人。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:34
translate chinese u20f_e6ca1864:

    # fr "I'm so happy you came home."
    fr "你回家了，我太高兴了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:35
translate chinese u20f_402e55b1:

    # fr "Let's go to bed. We can talk in the morning."
    fr "我们去睡觉吧。明天早上再聊。"

